{"tid":2187432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潔箎訪歐，西班牙冀加強中西關係，首相將安排到訪北京","createTime":"2020-09-03T15:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T15:36:29.000Z","uid":64191,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5c67b9e95840561605a3af4588d518397ebbc627","tid":2187432,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:16:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.prensa-latina.cu/index.php?o=rn&amp;id=393886&amp;SEO=espana-destaca-solidez-de-relaciones-con-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prensa-latina.cu%2Findex.php%3Fo%3Drn%26id%3D393886%26SEO%3Despana-destaca-solidez-de-relaciones-con-china&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjfY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=31e49686\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.prensa-latina.cu/index.php?o=rn&amp;id=393886&amp;SEO=espana-destaca-solidez-de-relaciones-con-china</a><br />\n<br />\n馬德里，9月3日（EFE）。-西班牙首相佩德羅&middot;山齊士（PedroS&aacute;nchez）本週四與中國共產黨外交事務委員會辦公室主任楊潔箎會面，他主張擴大援助範圍，與中國的貿易關係平衡，以及5G網絡部署的安全性。<br />\n<br />\n 在蒙羅拉宮舉行的會議上，山齊士強調了兩國之間戰略關係的&ldquo;巨大力量&rdquo;和重要性，並表示希望在兩國《聯合聲明》框架內深化全面戰略協會。2018年中國國家主席習近平在西班牙進行國事訪問，期間與西班牙簽署了協議。 <br />\n<br />\n根據政府的一份照會，山齊士還感謝中國政府為便利醫療用品的運輸所做的努力，以及在西班牙面對武漢肺炎最險峻既時候，所作的捐贈。<br />\n<br />\n 在會議上，山齊士和楊潔箎提出了在電動汽車、農業食品和旅遊業加強商業合作，後者是受到肺炎影響最大的部門。<br />\n<br />\n目前西班牙已選擇支持旅遊業，並促進開闢西班牙和中國主要城市之間的新直達路線。<br />\n<br />\n關於5G網絡的部署，西班牙認為確保最大條件的技術安全、數據訪問、自治和隱私下進行此類部署。與會二人還談到了兩國政府的利益，即在情況允許的情況下，山齊士正式訪問北京。  EFE<br />\n<br />\nLink係西班牙原文<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.prensa-latina.cu/images/2020/septiembre/03/w-china-espana2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prensa-latina.cu%2Fimages%2F2020%2Fseptiembre%2F03%2Fw-china-espana2.jpg&h=3e2d58fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e5040683c00add59c67482de4c60361901a386f","tid":2187432,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:17:33.000Z","msg":"屎冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df55c68f27a09fd0dd4c8abc4b70810458ea1635","tid":2187432,"uid":176313,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:20:20.000Z","msg":"垃圾西班牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbdc37a6c6255ff98806124bb04bbb3fbf7b1a03","tid":2187432,"uid":127454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:21:35.000Z","msg":"點解西班牙可以窮到係咁奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5f73f0da8be1b6bbdfd1309049d57fe16e71ba","tid":2187432,"uid":13745,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cbdc37a6c6255ff98806124bb04bbb3fbf7b1a03","tid":2187432,"uid":127454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:21:35.000Z","msg":"點解西班牙可以窮到係咁奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:23:00.000Z","msg":"失業率高<br />\n但係之前西班牙都有鞋商排華反華"},{"pid":"e71b8b63209f56bcc6237d8f23dd6fb1ed1ef4b3","tid":2187432,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:24:11.000Z","msg":"其實大部分國家都唔用華為設備 , 你仲走去用 , 過幾年新 6g 上場時好大機會被孤立 , 美國一定會專登唔兼容華為設備"},{"pid":"87048330bf716685e5d8f0f779828ccd77307eeb","tid":2187432,"uid":49184,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:25:11.000Z","msg":"不愧為歐洲支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3e4866ae3b06e135ca7fa5b2082a9fa33bbf49","tid":2187432,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:26:57.000Z","msg":"武肺死咁多人都仲要奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c34e6b11680a27c53de7ba58f5037336460861","tid":2187432,"uid":53705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:27:47.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得主要原因係 楊潔箎 態度好過王毅先<br />\n最起碼客客氣氣<br />\n<br />\n如果今次又係王毅去西班牙<br />\n肯定又 警告西班牙, 唔同中共 結盟就 付出沉重代價<br />\n然後西班牙政府 